@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
[*] --> Approved
Approved --> Pending : submit
Pending --> Archived : cancel
Pending : entry / log deposit
Archived --> Reviewed : process
Reviewed --> Processing : confirm
Approved --> Processing : revert
Processing --> [*]
@enduml